  "body": "Goal: remove peers that timeouts often\r\n\r\n- add peer liveness check service:\r\n   - periodically send ping request to peers\r\n   - store ping responses in peer store metadata book\r\n   - disconnect peers not responding to ping\r\n\r\nAdditional measures if those are timeouts only on block by range requests (my suspicion that these are shut down peers that aren't detected on libp2p side).\r\n",
